data.description: Upgraded 2 bedroom condo at the base of Heavenly and the famed Gunbarrel. This rare offering has an additional 200+ feet of loft space for extended friends and family. The kitchen has slab granite counters and newer appliances. Cozy up by the fire after skiing, or enjoy a warm summer night on the BBQ deck surrounded by old growth pines. This HOA boasts one of the best amenities package, including pool, hot tubs and clubhouse. The Summit Condominiums are located a short distance from world class dining, gaming and, of course, the natural beauty of Lake Tahoe. Bring your ski equipment and your tooth brush. This condo is offered turn key. 2019-05-20
